}}Win\n|19\u20131\n|align=left|{{flagicon|AZE}} [[Jamaladdin Magomedov]]\n|style=\"font-size:88%\"|6\u20131\n|style=\"font-size:88%\" rowspan=3|\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|18\u20131\n|align=left|{{flagicon|GEO}} [[Geno Petriashvili]]\n|style=\"font-size:88%\"| 6\u20133\n|-\n! style=background:white colspan=7 |\n[[2012 World University Championship \u2013 Men's freestyle 120 kg|2012 World University Championship]] {{gold1}} at 120&nbsp;kg\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|17\u20131\n|align=left|{{flagicon|IRI}} [[Parviz Hadi]]\n|style=\"font-size:88%\"|Tech Fall (10\u20130)\n|style=\"font-size:88%\" rowspan=5|October 2, 2012\n|style=\"font-size:88%\" rowspan=5|[[2012 World University Championship \u2013 Men's freestyle 120 kg|2012 World University Championship]]\n|style=\"text-align:left;font-size:88%;\" rowspan=5|{{flagicon|FIN}} [[Kuortane]]\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|16\u20131\n|align=left|{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Vitali Gagiev]]\n|style=\"font-size:88%\"|10\u20132\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|15\u20131\n|align=left|{{flagicon|USA}} Anthony Nelson\n|style=\"font-size:88%\"|Tech-Fall (9\u20130)\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|14\u20131\n|align=left|{{flagicon|MGL}} [[Odgerel Bat-Ochir]]\n|style=\"font-size:88%\"|7\u20130\n|-\n! style=background:white colspan=7 | [[Wrestling at the 2012 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's freestyle 120 kg|2012 Olympics Games]] 9th at 120&nbsp;kg\n|-\n|{{No2}}Loss\n|13\u20131\n|align=left|{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Bilyal Makhov]]\n|style=\"font-size:88%\"|1\u20130, 3\u20130\n|style=\"font-size:88%\" rowspan=2|August 11, 2012\n|style=\"font-size:88%\" rowspan=2|[[Wrestling at the 2012 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's freestyle 120 kg|2012 Olympics Games]]\n|style=\"text-align:left;font-size:88%;\" rowspan=2|{{flagicon|UK}} London\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|13\u20130\n|align=left|{{flagicon|UKR}} [[Oleksandr Khotsianivskyi]]\n|style=\"font-size:88%\"|1\u20130, 2\u20130\n|-\n|-\n! style=background:white colspan=7 | [[2012 Yasar Dogu \u2013 Men's Freestyle 120 kg|2012 Ya\u015far Do\u011fu tournament]] {{gold1}} at 1