comb]] (1899\u20131971)\n* [[David Farrar (actor)|David Farrar]] (1908\u20131995) (ashes scattered into the [[Indian Ocean]])\n* [[Jos\u00e9 Fern\u00e1ndez (pitcher)]] (1992\u20132016)\n* [[Virginia Field]] (1917\u20131992)\n* [[John Fiedler]] (1925\u20132005)\n* [[Paul Frees]] (1920-1986) (ashes sprinkled into the Pacific Ocean)\n* [[Victor French]] (1934\u20131989)\n* [[Benson Fong]] (1916\u20131987) \n* [[Bob Fosse]] (1927\u20131987)\n* [[Anne Francis]] (1930\u20132011)\n* [[Jean Gabin]] (1904\u20131976)\n* [[Jerry Garcia]] (1942\u20131995)\n* [[Erle Stanley Gardner]] (1899\u20131970)\n* [[Marvin Gaye]] (1938\u20131984)\n* [[Leyla Gencer]] (1928\u20132008) (cremated and ashes scattered off from [[Bosphorus]])\n* [[Lowell George]] (1945\u20131979)\n* [[Stan Getz]] (1927\u20131991)\n* [[Frances Gifford]] (1920\u20131994) \n* [[Tulsi Giri]] (1926\u20132018)\n* [[Hermann G\u00f6ring]] (1893\u20131946)\n* [[Michael Gough]] (1916\u20132011)  (ashes scattered into the English Channel)\n* [[Cary Grant]] (1904\u20131986)\n* [[Virginia Grey]] (1917\u20132004)\n* [[Charlotte Greenwood]] (1890\u20131977)\n* [[Alan Hale Jr.]] (1921\u20131990)\n* [[Rusty Hamer]] (1947\u20131990)\n* [[Alaina Reed Hall]] (1946\u20132009) \n* [[Neil Hamilton (actor)|Neil Hamilton]] (1899\u20131984)\n* [[Yip Harburg]] (1896\u20131981)\n* [[Harman and Ising|Hugh Harman]] (1903-1982)\n* [[John Hart (actor)]] (1917\u20132009)\n* [[Paul Hartman]] (1904\u20131973)\n* [[Phil Hartman]] (1948\u20131998) (ashes scattered off from [[Santa Catalina Island, California|Santa Catalina Island]]'s Emerald Bay)\n* [[Walter de Havilland]] (1872\u20131968)\n* [[Kenneth Hawks]] (1898\u20131930)\n* [[Richard Haydn]] (1905\u20131985)\n* [[Jean Heather]] (1921\u20131995)\n* [[Robert A. Heinlein]] (1907\u20131988) (cremated and ashes scattered in the [[Pacific Ocean]]) <ref>[http://www.heinleinsociety.org/rah/biographies.html Heinlein Society<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>\n* [[Henrik, Prince Consort of Denmark]] (19